'''ISO 3166-2:AM''' codes for the [[provinces of Armenia]]. The purpose of this family of standards is to establish a worldwide series of short abbreviations for places, for use on package labels, containers and such. Anywhere where a short alphanumeric code can serve to clearly indicate a location in a more convenient and less ambiguous form than the full place name. 

== Provinces (10) ==

* AM-AG	[[Aragac̣otn]]
* AM-AR	[[Ararat]]
* AM-AV	[[Armavir]]
* AM-ER	[[ISO 3166-2:Erevan|Erevan]] (city)
* AM-GR	[[Geġark'unik']]
* AM-KT	[[Kotayk']]
* AM-LO	[[Loṙy]]
* AM-SH	[[Širak]]
* AM-SU	[[Syunik']]
* AM-TV	[[Tavuš]]
* AM-VD	[[Vayoc Jor]]


